des:
Welcome to the Ramayan Quiz.
-Ramayan is one of the greatest sanskrit epic.
-To start this skill say, 'Alexa, open Ramayan Quiz'.
-This skill asks you 10 questions about Ramayan and in the end scores you out of 10.
-This skill has over 50+ questions about Ramayan.
-Right review what problem you are facing in the app or what improvement you want.
